2026-03-28T07:25:25.749235Z I ext-firestore-send-email-processqueue: {"message":"Sending via transport.sendMail()","mailOptions":{"bcc":[],"from":"platform@tektrakker.com","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>TekAir Inc. - Spring AC Tune-Up Special</title>\n    <style>\n        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {\n            .email-container {\n                width: 100% !important;\n                margin: auto !important;\n                border-radius: 0 !important;\n            }\n            .content-padding {\n                padding: 20px 15px !important;\n            }\n            .mobile-text-center {\n                text-align: center !important;\n            }\n            .title-text {\n                font-size: 24px !important;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7f6; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: #333333;\">\n\n    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background-color: #f4f7f6; padding: 40px 10px;\">\n        <tr>\n            <td align=\"center\">\n                \n                <!-- Main Email Container -->\n                <table class=\"email-container\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\">\n                    \n                    <!-- Header / Logo Area -->\n                    <tr>\n                        <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding: 30px 20px; background-color: #ffffff; border-bottom: 4px solid #0ea5e9;\">\n                            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/220x65/ffffff/0ea5e9?text=TekAir+Inc.\" alt=\"TekAir Inc. Professional Home Services\" width=\"220\" style=\"display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border: 0;\">\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                    <!-- Hero Section -->\n                    <tr>\n                        <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding: 40px 30px 25px 30px; background-color: #f0f9ff;\">\n                            <h1 class=\"title-text\" style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 28px; color: #0369a1; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px;\">\n                                Spring is Here. Is Your AC Ready for the Heat?\n                            </h1>\n                            <p style=\"margin: 15px 0 0 0; font-size: 18px; color: #0c4a6e; line-height: 1.5;\">\n                                Beat the summer rush and keep your home perfectly chilled.\n                            </p>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n\n                    <!-- Body Content -->\n                    <tr>\n                        <td class=\"content-padding\" style=\"padding: 35px 40px;\">\n                            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563;\">\n                                Hello Neighbor,\n                            </p>\n                            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563;\">\n                                As the weather warms up, the last thing you want is a surprise breakdown when you need your air conditioning the most. A professional spring maintenance check not only extends the life of your unit but also ensures it runs efficiently—saving you money on your monthly energy bills!\n                            </p>\n                            \n                            <!-- Highlighted Offer Box -->\n                            <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"background-color: #f8fafc; border: 2px dashed #0ea5e9; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding: 30px 20px;\">\n                                        <h2 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 20px; color: #0284c7; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;\">Exclusive Spring Special</h2>\n                                        <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; color: #0ea5e9; line-height: 1;\">\n                                            $99\n                                        </p>\n                                        <p style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #475569;\">\n                                            Comprehensive AC Tune-Up\n                                        </p>\n                                        <p style=\"margin: 5px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;\">\n                                            <em>(Limited time offer for our local residents)</em>\n                                        </p>\n                                    </td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n\n                            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 30px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #4b5563;\">\n                                Our expert technicians at TekAir Inc. will thoroughly inspect, clean, and optimize your cooling system so you can enjoy worry-free comfort all season long.\n                            </p>\n\n                            <!-- Call To Action Button -->\n                            <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td align=\"center\">\n                                        <a href=\"tel:2105442720\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 18px 36px; background-color: #0ea5e9; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 50px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.25);\">\n                                            Claim Your $99 Tune-Up\n                                        </a>\n                                    </td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n                            \n                            <p style=\"margin: 25px 0 0 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #64748b; text-align: center;\">\n                                Prefer to book via email? Reply directly to <a href=\"mailto:rvavrecan@tekairinc.com\" style=\"color: #0ea5e9; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600;\">rvavrecan@tekairinc.com</a>\n                            </p>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n\n                    <!-- Footer -->\n                    <tr>\n                        <td style=\"padding: 35px 30px; background-color: #0f172a; color: #94a3b8; text-align: center;\">\n                            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: #f8fafc; letter-spacing: 0.5px;\">\n                                TekAir Inc.\n                            </p>\n                            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;\">\n                                Professional Home Services<br>\n                                Delivering total comfort and peace of mind.\n                            </p>\n                            <p style=\"margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px;\">\n                                <a href=\"tel:2105442720\" style=\"color: #38bdf8; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">(210) 544-2720</a> \n                                <span style=\"color: #475569; margin: 0 10px;\">|</span> \n                                <a href=\"mailto:rvavrecan@tekairinc.com\" style=\"color: #38bdf8; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;\">Contact Us</a>\n                            </p>\n                            <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n                                <tr>\n                                    <td style=\"border-top: 1px solid #1e293b; padding-top: 20px;\">\n                                        <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5;\">\n                                            &copy; 2024 TekAir Inc. All rights reserved.<br>\n                                            You received this email because you've trusted us with your home services.\n                                        </p>\n                                    </td>\n                                </tr>\n                            </table>\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                    \n                </table>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n\n</body>\n</html>","cc":[],"to":["hlynch1224@gmail.com","changismith4@gmail.com","klayman0327@gmail.com"],"subject":"This is a test!"}}
